<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT58">
<l>eṉṉeñca mēyāṉ iruḷnīkki yempirāṉ</l>
<l>maṉṉañca muṉṉoruṉāḷ maṇṇaḷantā ṉeṉṉeñca</l>
<l>mēyāṉai yillā viṭaiyēṟṟāṉ vevviṉaitīrt</l>
<l>tāyāṉuk kākkiṉē ṉaṉpu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I have produced love for Him who lives in my heart,</l>
<l>our Lord the Dispeller of darkness, Him who, one day in the past, measured the earth</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the kings were afraid,</l>
<l>Him who lives in my heart, Him who flourished by ending the cruel karman</l>
<l rend="indent">of [Śiva] on the bull who does not have [Him in his heart].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
